1
00:00:36,300 --> 00:00:40,180
=The Best Man=

2
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:42,500
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,030
Where's my grandma?

4
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:51,670
Grandma went back to Panlong City.

5
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:54,070
So, you tricked me into coming here.

6
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:55,910
Tricked you?

7
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:59,079
Even though Chen Yue
is now in the vegetative state,

8
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:00,920
his subordinates have always misbehaved.

9
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,480
They have been inciting rebellions
in the Chen Family's side branches.

10
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:05,840
That's why Grandma had to return
and take charge for that.

11
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,710
Chen Zhuo,

12
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,150
I know

13
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,950
you're worried about Grandma too.

14
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,150
You're a filial child.

15
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:22,000
Please go back as soon as possible
and take over the patriarch position.

16
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,270
Don't make Grandma worry.

17
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,470
Even if I inherit
the patriarch's position,

18
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:28,479
I won't marry you.

19
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:31,030
The Chen Family values
promise above all else.

20
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:33,199
If you don't fulfill your promise,

21
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:36,799
I doubt you won't be in the
patriarch's position for long.

22
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,950
How ridiculous!

23
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:40,590
I'd never use my marriage

24
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:43,030
to secure my status as the patriarch.

25
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,910
Chen Zhuo,

26
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,270
you can only be mine.

27
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,039
Dad,

28
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:22,750
where are we going?

29
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,670
Of course, we're moving abroad.

30
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,639
The Chen Family
has acquired Wanlong Hotel,

31
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:28,830
with the condition that our
entire family migrated abroad.

32
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:32,519
I don't want to go. I dedicate all my
hard work to Wanlong Hotel.

33
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,560
I don't want to go anywhere.

34
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,600
The hotel can be exchanged
for a large sum of money.

35
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,990
With that money,
you can find any man you want.

36
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,590
I don't want anyone else.
I only want Chen Zhuo.

37
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,239
Dad,

38
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,830
stop the car.

39
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,199
Chen Zhuo?

40
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,590
It's the Chen Family who drugged you.

41
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:48,160
You still insist on
wanting to be with him.

42
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,190
Don't force me!

43
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,590
Hey!

44
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:53,630
If you dare to force me again,
I'll end my life right here.

45
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,550
None of you will get
to leave the country.

46
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,559
Xu Meiying.

47
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,550
Go ahead to stab yourself to death.

48
00:02:58,600 --> 00:02:59,359
Let go of me.

49
00:02:59,360 --> 00:02:59,839
Stop it!

50
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,550
Let go of...

51
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,790
Hey, Xu Meiying!

52
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,039
If you get down the car,

53
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:11,390
you won't be able to see your dad again
once we move abroad.

54
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,750
Dad.

55
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,110
Xu Meiying!

56
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:48,939
♪The sky waits for the fog to lift,
like ears longing for answers♪

57
00:03:48,940 --> 00:03:56,370
♪The one who can't see the truth
continues to struggle♪

58
00:03:56,720 --> 00:04:04,190
♪Words once spoken turn to scars,
love isn't etched before hairs turn grey♪

59
00:04:04,380 --> 00:04:11,810
♪Yet it doesn't hinder me
from gazing at you till the end♪

60
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:19,459
♪Whose voice climbs
desperately into dreams?♪

61
00:04:19,460 --> 00:04:26,659
♪Awakened in tranquility,
and the time whispers, "Let it go"♪

62
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:30,530
♪I've waited through spring rain
to evaporate in the summer♪

63
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,430
- Chen Zhuo!
- Don't move!

64
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,430
Let me go.

65
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,670
Even if I let you go now, it's too late.

66
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,030
By now,

67
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:52,910
Xu Meiying is already
on a flight abroad.

68
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,150
Meiying...

69
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:03,930
♪My right eye twitched with luck♪

70
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,959
Xu Meiying.

71
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:06,679
Chen Zhuo.

72
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,950
You must wait for me.

73
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,550
Where are you?

74
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:22,130
♪Told me not to be stubborn,
how thoughtful of you♪

75
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:27,739
♪As if I've always been unworthy♪

76
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:33,059
♪It doesn't matter
if you forget me someday♪

77
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:38,619
♪How fragile my words sound
when I say I don't love you♪

78
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:48,079
♪I let you go and set you free,
but how can I free myself?♪

79
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,230
Xu Meiying,

80
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,870
sorry to keep you waiting.

81
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,070
Chen Zhuo,

82
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,910
is it you?

83
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:02,219
♪I can find solace♪

84
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:06,619
♪Knowing someone else
loses sleep at night♪

85
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:12,450
♪Even a faint love can still feel grand♪

86
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,190
I miss you a lot.

87
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:30,899
♪I can survive lonely nights
choking back silent tears♪

88
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:35,579
♪Tears of maturity
surrender to loneliness♪

89
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:40,570
♪Blurring the memories of the past♪

