loses sleep at night♪

97
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,990
Good day, Ms. Yin.

98
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,910
Yes.

99
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,430
(As long as Wanlong Hotel
is in my hands,)

100
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,990
(Chen Zhuo,)

101
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,670
(you won't be able to escape.)

102
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,759
Every shareholders,

103
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,119
from today onwards,

104
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:47,990
I am the new chairperson
of Wanlong Hotel,

105
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,310
Yin Muzi.

106
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,430
Everybody,

107
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,510
Wanlong Hotel's owner

108
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,750
can only be someone with the surname Xu.

109
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,430
Greetings, Ms, Xu.

110
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,710
Xu Meiying,

111
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,630
you didn't board the plane after all.

112
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,639
I still hold my shares in Wanlong Hotel.

113
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,030
How could I leave?

114
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,879
I'm here

115
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,199
to reclaim the right
to manage the hotel.

116
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,510
Too bad.

117
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:18,350
Your parents sold their shares to me

118
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,870
at three times the market price.

119
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:24,830
Now, I'm the largest
shareholder of Wanlong Hotel.

120
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:30,110
(Share Transfer Agreement)
The hotel's management rights are on me.

121
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:33,770
(Share Transfer Agreement)

122
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,790
Is that even a big deal?

123
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,910
Yin Muzi,

124
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,910
Jiangnan Group is the second
largest shareholder of Wanlong Hotel.

125
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:48,199
With the shares holding
by Jiangnan Group and Meiying,

126
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,559
the management rights belong to us.

127
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,479
You?

128
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,870
Step aside.

129
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,590
Muzi,

130
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,750
listen to me.

131
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,430
Return to Panlong City.

132
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,350
Chen Zhuo,

133
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,710
you'll regret this.

134
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,670
Huang Yuhuan,

135
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,919
thank you.

136
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:18,430
Don't mention it, Meiying.

137
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,519
Now, we should decide

138
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:23,350
on a new chairperson.

139
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,319
Chen Zhuo knows the hotel
management better than I do.

140
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,359
I nominate Chen Zhuo

141
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,630
as the next chairperson
of Wanlong Group.

142
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,990
I agree!

143
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,479
Agree!

144
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,630
Agree!

145
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,750
I disagree.

146
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,519
I said

147
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,319
Wanlong Hotel could only
carry the surname Xu.

148
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,919
I'm nothing more than

149
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,390
a humble security guard
by Ms. Xu's side.

